{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "b78d2b2c-63e2-4c9f-863a-8677c7f763a1",
		"name": "Primrose Backend API",
		"description": "Collection for testing Primrose Backend endpoints.\n\n### Authentication\n- **JWT Auth**: Used for admin endpoints. Obtain token via `/api/auth/login` and it will be stored in the `jwt_token` variable. Tokens expire in 1 day.\n- **TOTP Auth**: Used for the public `/api/pages` endpoint. Uses the `X-App-Auth` header. Note: Postman doesn't natively generate TOTP codes without scripts or external libraries, so you'll need to provide it manually in the variable.\n- **Health Token**: Used for `/health` via `X-Health-Token` header.\n\n### Token Expiration\nIf a request returns a `401 Unauthorized` and the `X-Token-Expired` header is `true`, the `jwt_token` variable is automatically cleared in the collection test script, signaling that a re-login is required.",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
	"item": [
		{
			"name": "Auth",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "Admin Login",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
									"if (jsonData.token) {",
									"    pm.collectionVariables.set(\"jwt_token\", jsonData.token);",
									"}"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n    \"username\": \"{{admin_username}}\",\n    \"password\": \"{{admin_password}}\"\n}",
							"options": {
								"raw": {
									"language": "json"
								}
							}
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login",
							"host": [
								"{{baseUrl}}"
							],
							"path": [
								"api",
								"auth",
								"login"
							]
						}
					},
					"response": []
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"name": "Public",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "Health Check",
					"request": {
						"method": "GET",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "X-Health-Token",
								"value": "{{health_token}}",
								"type": "text"
							}
						],
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/health",
							"host": [
								"{{baseUrl}}"
							],
							"path": [
								"health"
							]
						}
					},
					"response": []
				},
				{
					"name": "Get Pages (TOTP)",
					"request": {
						"method": "GET",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "X-App-Auth",
								"value": "{{totp_code}}",
								"description": "6-digit TOTP code generated from SharedSecret",
								"type": "text"
							}
						],
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/pages",
							"host": [
								"{{baseUrl}}"
							],
							"path": [
								"api",
								"pages"
							]
						},
						"description": "Requires TOTP code in X-App-Auth header. You can use a tool like Google Authenticator or an online TOTP generator with your `SharedSecret`."
					},
					"response": []
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"name": "Admin (JWT)",
			"item": [
